com.facebook.buck.core.graph.transformation

Interface GraphTransformer<Key,Result>

  • Type Parameters:
    Key - The types of Keys used to query for the result on the graph computation
    Result - The result of the computation given a specific key

    public interface GraphTransformer<Key,Result>
    Interface for transformations with the GraphTransformationEngine.

    The transformation is guaranteed the following conditions:

    • 1. transform(Object, TransformationEnvironment) is only called once per key if caching is enabled.
    • 2. transform(Object, TransformationEnvironment) is only called after all keys in discoverDeps(Object) has been computed.
